        </div>
        <div class="cg-process-step">
          <div class="cg-step-top">
            <div class="cg-step-num">2</div>
            <div class="cg-step-connector"></div>
          </div>
          <h3>Proof of Concept</h3>
          <p>Build a focused prototype to validate the approach and demonstrate feasibility.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cg-process-step">
          <div class="cg-step-top">
            <div class="cg-step-num">3</div>
            <div class="cg-step-connector"></div>
          </div>
          <h3>MVP</h3>
          <p>Develop a working product with core features ready for real-world testing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cg-process-step">
          <div class="cg-step-top">
            <div class="cg-step-num">4</div>
            <div class="cg-step-connector"></div>
          </div>
