          <p>Yes. We integrate with your current tools, platforms, and data sources. We're stack-agnostic and work with whatever fits your infrastructure and policies.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="cg-faq-item">
          <summary>What industries do you work with?</summary>
          <p>We've delivered across manufacturing, infrastructure, energy, and professional services. Our process applies to any sector where AI can streamline operations or unlock data.</p>
